tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE website_traffic (    id INT PRIMARY KEY,    user_id INT,    page_id INT,    timestamp TIMESTAMP,    activity_type VARCHAR(50) )

CREATE TABLE website_traffic (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    page_url VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    visit_date DATE NOT NULL,
    visit_time TIME NOT NULL,
    user_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE website_visits (
  visit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  page_visited VARCHAR(255),
  duration_in_seconds INT
)

CREATE TABLE ad_placements (
  ad_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  placement_name VARCHAR(255),
  ad_type VARCHAR(50),
  cost_per_impression DECIMAL(10,2),
  impressions_count INT
)

CREATE TABLE user_engagement (
  engagement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  page_visited VARCHAR(255),
  engagement_duration_seconds INT,
  engagement_type VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE ad_clicks (
  click_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  ad_id INT,
  user_id INT,
  click_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  click_location VARCHAR(255)
)
